{
  "stem": "13096.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the next day, the-- the manager called me in his office, say, you can start working, but the only thing we are not going to tell Rome that you-- we've got a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were paying me my salary in cash and nobody knew I was working there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after a while, those girls, one by one, they all left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They went to Italy because the bombardment and the situation in Rhodes Island become very critical.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So later on, I become the manager myself, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But no, in-- in Italy, they didn't know I was there and I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You mentioned the bombardments.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Can you explain what you mean by that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It means that, you know, we live in this island, Rhodes Island, which is the Juderia, which is the Jewish quarters that you call the ghetto in Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were called the Juderia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody wants to live in the Juderia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not obliged to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We can go and live anywhere or wherever the center is, but we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews want to be next to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were just in that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It happened that the Juderia was the nearest-- the nearest part of the island next to the port.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So now, during the war, there were lots of ships and all these, you know, like German ships, Italian ships in the port were bringing and taking out the soldiers, you know, there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Imagine that during the time, you know, the population of Rhodes Island, it consist of, like, 40,000.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But during the war, we had 90,000 to 100,000 soldiers, all the Germans and Italians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there were a lot of traffic and lots of thing in the port.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
